polixeni papapetrou (21 november 1960 – 11 january 2018) was a greek singer, songwriter, and actress. papapetrou was born in athens, greece. she started her music career in the early 1980s as the lead vocalist of the pop-rock band "polixeni". the band released two albums, before disbanding in 1984. papapetrou later pursued a solo career, and released her first album, "poi einai" in 1991. the album achieved moderate success, and spawned two hit singles: "oti" and "to hrono i pou". in 1997, papapetrou released her second album, "ana genas". the album was more successful than her previous effort, and spawned
washūyama yoshikazu (born 2 april 1949 as yoshikazu washūyama) is a japanese artist who is internationally known for his ink drawings. yoshikazu washūyama was born in 1949 in numazu city, shizuoka prefecture, japan. after graduating from high school, he studied at the osaka school of arts and crafts from 1970 to 1973. he then studied at the university of tokyo from 1973 to 1975, and at the royal college of art in london from 1975 to 1978. from 1978 to 1984 he was a professor at the tokyo university of the arts. yoshikazu washūyama's art is based on ink drawings
sacha noam baron cohen (born 13 october 1971) is an english comedian, actor, and writer. he is known for his work on the television series da ali g show, borat, and brüno. sacha baron cohen was born in england to a jewish family. he was educated at a secondary school in north london and at the university of edinburgh, where he studied political science. baron cohen began his career as a stand-up comic and appeared on british television shows such as the eleven o'clock show, never mind the buzzcocks, and have i got news for you. he then became known
the chelsea physic garden was established as a public garden in 1729 and is the oldest botanical garden in london. the garden comprises a variety of gardens including a arboretum, a herb garden, and a rose garden. the gardens are open to the public from april to september. the chelsea physic garden was established as a public garden in 1729 by the 3rd earl of bute. the garden was initially known as the earl of bute's garden but was renamed the chelsea physic garden in 1739. the garden comprises a variety of gardens including a arboretum, a herb garden, and
the ozieri culture (or san michele culture) is a neolithic culture that flourished in the central apennines region of italy about 11,200 years ago. it is one of the earliest known european neolithic cultures, and is particularly noted for its painted pottery. the ozieri culture is named after the archaeological site of san michele di ozieri, where its characteristic pottery was first found. the ozieri culture is thought to have emerged around 11,200 years ago and lasted until about 7,500 years ago. it was characterised by the production of painted pottery, which has been found all over the region where
in mathematics, a limit point (or cluster point, or point of inflection, or simply limit) is a point at which the derivative of a function becomes zero. a limit point is a point at which the derivative of a function becomes zero. this happens when the function approaches some fixed point from either the left or right. in more general terms, a limit point is any point where the curvature of a surface or curve is zero. the concept of a limit point can be applied to many different types of functions, including polynomial functions, exponential functions, and differential equations.
"kiss goodnight" is the debut single released by american singer-songwriter and record producer charlie puth. it was released on may 5, 2017, by atlantic records. the song was written by puth, along with jacob kasher and brian burton, and produced by puth. the song is about a relationship that is coming to an end. the lyrics are about loving someone farewell and wishing them goodnight. it has been described as an "emotionally charged ballad" with a "deeply romantic" message. "kiss goodnight" reached number one on the us billboard hot 100 chart and became puth's first number-one single in the united
afterimage is a filipino rock band who gained popularity in the late 1990s. formed in 1995, the band originally consisted of lead vocalist/guitarist john lloyd cruz, drummer fuzzy acuna, bassist/backing vocalist joey de leon, and keyboardist rickey padilla. afterimage released their self-titled debut album in 1997, which peaked at number two on the philippine albums chart. the following year, they released their second album, entitled "afterimage 2". in 2000, they released their third album, "afterimage 3", which spawned the hit single "kung paano". in 2001, the band released their fourth album, "afterimage 4". the album peaked at number one on
the philippine albums chart. in 2002, they released their fifth album, "afterimage 5". the album spawned the hit singles "pag-ibig sa mi" and "2am". in 2003, de leon departed from the band to pursue a solo career. cruz then recruited new members: lead guitarist reynaldo blanco (formerly of zz top), bassist rey galvez (formerly of the dawn), and drummer marvin legaspi (formerly of sponge). they released their sixth album, "afterimage 6", in 2004. the album spawned the hit singles "nasaan ka na?" and "kahit ibin". in 2005, they released their seventh album, "afterimage 7", which spawned the hit singles "una
franny armstrong (born 3 february 1972) is a scottish singer, songwriter and record producer. franny armstrong was born in glasgow on 3 february 1972, the daughter of singer and songwriter sandy armstrong and american musician gary louris. she started her career as a backing vocalist for her father, touring with him and appearing on his albums throughout the early 1990s. in 1992, she released her debut album "sandy", which reached number 37 on the uk albums chart. armstrong's second album, "lucky", was released in 1995 and produced by her father, who wrote all the songs. the album reached number 49
on the uk albums chart. in 1997, she released her third album "the gospel according to stray dog", which peaked at number 43 on the uk albums chart. in 2003, armstrong released her fourth album "strange fruit", which reached number 71 on the uk albums chart. the following year, she released her fifth album "the weight of these wings". the album reached number 47 on the uk albums chart. in 2006, she released her sixth album "these are the days". the album reached number 63 on the uk albums chart. in 2007, she released her seventh album "the laughing policeman".
william starke rosecrans (september 6, 1819march 11, 1898) was an american general and republican politician who served as the 18th united states secretary of war from 1864 to 1868 and as the 21st governor of missouri from 1869 to 1875. william rosecrans was born in lebanon, ohio, on september 6, 1819. he was raised in a military family, the son of colonel james rosecrans and the grandson of general james k. polk. after studying at the united states military academy and west point, rosecrans graduated in 1843 and was commissioned a second lieutenant in the army corps of engineers. he
served in various engineering assignments throughout the united states before being stationed in texas during the mexican-american war. rosecrans played a leading role in the american victory over mexico and was promoted to first lieutenant in march 1847. in may 1850, he was assigned to lead a new engineering regiment, the first u.s. infantry, which he later raised to full regimental size and re-titled the sixth u.s. infantry. he served with this unit during the oregon war (1846–1848) and in the mexican–american war (1846–1848), earning distinction at churubusco and cerro gordo. after returning from mexico, rosecrans served under general winfield
bastien charles patrick héry (born 23 march 1984) is a french professional footballer who plays as a defender for english club swansea city and the france national team. héry was born in pau, pyrénées-atlantiques. he started his career at hometown club pau fc before moving to sc bastia in 2003. he spent three seasons at bastia, making over 100 appearances for the club, before moving to lille in 2007. he spent four seasons at lille, helping them to two ligue 1 titles and two coupe de france trophies. in 2014, he joined swansea city for £5 million. héry has represented
