the frenulum of tongue or tongue web is a small band of tissue that hangs down from the roof of the mouth on either side of the frenulum linguae, a fold of mucous membrane that separates the tongue from the floor of the mouth. the frenulum of tongue is responsible for controlling the position of the tongue. the frenulum can be easily felt by gently pulling it between the thumb and first two fingers. it can be elongated or shortened by massaging it with a finger, and can be removed surgically in rare cases when it becomes lodged in a
lou taylor pucci (born july 27, 1985) is an american musician, singer and songwriter. he is the lead vocalist, guitarist and main songwriter for the rock band my chemical romance. pucci has also released two solo albums, the strange and beautiful world of lou taylor pucci (2010) and black messiah (2016). pucci was born in bensalem, pennsylvania, to patricia (née lindquist), a nurse, and lou pucci, a truck driver. he has two sisters, one older and one younger. pucci's parents divorced when he was young and he lived with his mother until she passed away from cancer in 2010. pucci
