anthony steven weiss am phd frsc ftse is an australian-born israeli mathematician who has made contributions to mathematics, theoretical computer science and physics. anthony weiss was born in sydney, australia on june 3, 1947. he received his undergraduate degree from the university of sydney in 1967, and his doctorate from the university of cambridge in 1974. after a year as a postdoctoral fellow at the university of california at berkeley, he moved to israel in 1975 and has since held faculty positions at tel aviv university and hebrew university of jerusalem. in 2006 he was appointed the inaugural chairman of
